📌 HOW TO USE THIS SOFTWARE

1. Run the main executable (IDM Trial Manager v1.2.0.exe)
2. If IDM is not installed, click "Download IDM" to visit the official site
3. After installation, choose one of three options:
   - "Freeze Trial": Permanently freeze the 30-day trial period (Recommended)
   - "Get Serial": Get a 180-day serial key (May show fake serial nag screen)
   - "Reset Now": Reset activation and trial keys

NOTE: For best results, run as administrator.

